    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a> * <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a> * Fail-Hard</b>\n</p><p><b>Fail-Hard</b> is a term related to an <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a> like <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">search</a>, to make <a href=\"/Alpha\" title=\"Alpha\">Alpha</a> and <a href=\"/Beta\" title=\"Beta\">Beta</a> <b>hard</b> <a href=\"/Bound\" title=\"Bound\">bounds</a> of the returned value of the search. Even <a href=\"/Terminal_Node\" title=\"Terminal Node\">terminal nodes</a> which indicate draw or mate scores are supposed to be adjusted on the hard alpha-beta bounds.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Fail-Hard_Condition\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Fail-Hard Condition</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Fail-Hard_Condition\">Fail-Hard Condition</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fail-Hard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Fail-Hard Condition\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<pre><a href=\"/Alpha\" title=\"Alpha\">Alpha</a> &lt;= <a href=\"/Score\" title=\"Score\">Score</a> &lt;= <a href=\"/Beta\" title=\"Beta\">Beta</a>\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fail-Hard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">Fail-High</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Fail-Low\" title=\"Fail-Low\">Fail-Low</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fail-Hard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fail-Hard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=136488\">Fail-soft or Fail-hard&#160;?</a> by <a href=\"/Teerapong_Tovirat\" title=\"Teerapong Tovirat\">Teerapong Tovirat</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 04, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=363710\">Fail-hard, fail-soft question</a> by <a href=\"/Dan_Honeycutt\" title=\"Dan Honeycutt\">Dan Honeycutt</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 06, 2004</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fail-Hard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=24954\">fail soft vs fail hard</a> by <a href=\"/Matthew_Lai\" title=\"Matthew Lai\">cyberfish</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 19, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30333\">Return eval or upper bound?</a> by <a href=\"/John_Merlino\" title=\"John Merlino\">John Merlino</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 26, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fail-Hard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48274\">First post (and FailHigh question!)</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Natale_Galioto&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Natale Galioto (page does not exist)\">Natale Galioto</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 14, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">Fail-High</a>, <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51284\">Fail soft vs fail hard</a> by <a href=\"/Sergei_Markoff\" title=\"Sergei Markoff\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a>, <a href=\"/Fail-Low\" title=\"Fail-Low\">Fail-Low</a>, <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fail-Hard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=79223\">Fail hard/soft</a> by Philippe Chevalier, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 28, 2022</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fail-Hard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alpha%E2%80%93beta_pruning#Pseudocode\">Alpha–beta pruning from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.ics.uci.edu/~eppstein/180a/990202b.html\">Lecture notes for February 2, 1999  Variants of Alpha-Beta Search</a> by <a href=\"/David_Eppstein\" title=\"David Eppstein\">David Eppstein</a></li>